summary: Adds a Small Cottage that lays near Rorikstead.
descriptionHtml:
A lore friendly home that lays near Rorikstead, you will find it in your map under the name \'Tundra Cottage\'. Inside you will find an enchanting table, alchemy table, cooking pot, fire, food and other necessities. If there are any glitches, please address so that I can fix them.

Thank you.

-Fixed TNP_update esm not in files anymore.
